## Description
The&nbsp;**Process Content **task allows to execute custom Java or Python code.

## Configuration
![](data:image/png;base64,)

- In the&nbsp;**Alias** field, enter the name of the task that will be displayed in the workflow.

- Click on the **Program &gt;**&nbsp;**Resource** field and select the On-Demand Program resource to use.

> Note

For more information, see:&nbsp;[On-Demand Program Resource Reference](/doxee-platform/docs/on-demand-program-resource-reference)

- *(optional)* To add a **Variable**, click ![](data:image/png;base64,) (**Add**) and fill in the required fields.![](data:image/png;base64,)

Enter the&nbsp;**Name** of the&nbsp;new variable.

- Enter the&nbsp;**Value** to assign to the new variable.
